title: BSÍ - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents BSÍ performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 4, 2022.

Songs:
My knee against kyriarchy
Vesturbæjar Beach
New Moon
Jelly Belly

Sigurlaug Thorarensen - Vocals / Drums
Julius Pollux Rothlaender - Synths / Bass

Host: Larry Mizell, Jr.
Audio Engineer: Jon Roberts
Audio Mastering: Kevin Suggs
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro & Scott Holpainen
Editor: Carlos Cruz
